com.ibm.caas

Class CAASProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.caas.CAASProperties

  • public class CAASProperties
extends Object
    This class provides an enumeration of the names of the properties supported for content items and project items.

    Content items support the following properties:

    • id
    • name
    • authors
    • title
    • authtemplateid
    • authtemplatename
    • authtemplatetitle
    • categories
    • contenttype
    • creationdate
    • creator
    • currentstage
    • description
    • expirydate
    • keywords
    • lastmodifieddate
    • lastmodifier
    • libraryid
    • libraryname
    • librarytitle
    • parentid
    • parentname
    • parenttitle
    • projectid
    • projectname
    • projecttitle
    • publishdate
    • status
    • statusid

    Project items support the following properties:

    • name
    • title
    • creationdate
    • creator
    • itemcount
    • lastmodifier
    • state
    • uuid
